{
  "date_key": "2026-03-22",
  "date_cn": "2026年03月22日",
  "day_cn": "周日",
  "english": "<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"background:#e8f0fe;border-left:4px solid #1a73e8;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:15px\">【今日主题】</strong><span style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:400;color:#1a73e8\">知识与学习（Knowledge, Curiosity, Growth）</span></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"background:#e3f2fd;border-left:4px solid #0d47a1;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#0d47a1;font-size:15px\">【英文原文】</strong></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Hey, so I heard you&#x27;ve been <strong>going down a rabbit hole</strong> with that online course on behavioral economics. How&#x27;s that going?</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Dude, I&#x27;m <span style=\"background:#f5f0e6;color:#8b7355;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.98em\">obsessed</span>. I started it just to <strong>brush up on</strong> some basics for work, but now I&#x27;m like six modules deep and watching YouTube lectures at 2 a.m. I honestly can&#x27;t stop.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Ha, that tracks. You&#x27;ve always been the type to <strong>geek out</strong> over random stuff. Remember when you spent an entire summer trying to <strong>get the hang of</strong> coding?</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Okay, fair point. But this time it&#x27;s different. The professor breaks things down so well — like, even the heavy theoretical stuff, she doesn&#x27;t <strong>talk over your head</strong> at all. She uses real-world examples, memes, the whole deal.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">That&#x27;s the dream. I had a stats professor in college who was brilliant but completely impossible to follow. Everything just went <strong>in one ear and out the other</strong> because he&#x27;d just drone on with no context.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Yeah, a good teacher makes all the difference. Honestly, the biggest thing I&#x27;ve learned so far is that I was just <strong>scratching the surface</strong> before. I thought I had a decent handle on economics, but turns out I barely knew anything.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Well, at least you&#x27;re <strong>putting in the work</strong> now. Most people just complain about not knowing stuff but never actually do anything about it. You&#x27;re out here doing the thing.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Thanks, man. I&#x27;m trying. The one downside is I keep bringing it up at dinner and my wife is like, &quot;Please, not again.&quot; I think she&#x27;s <strong>sick and tired of</strong> hearing about loss aversion and sunk cost fallacy.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Ha! Classic. But hey, you know what they say — <strong>knowledge is power</strong>. Just maybe don&#x27;t <strong>pick her brain</strong> about nudge theory over pasta, you know?</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Yeah yeah, <span style=\"background:#f5f0e6;color:#8b7355;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.98em\">point taken</span>. I&#x27;ll save it for you instead.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">Lucky me.</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"background:#e8f5e9;border-left:4px solid #1b5e20;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#1b5e20;font-size:15px\">【中文翻译】</strong></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">嘿，我听说你最近一直在<strong>深入钻研</strong>（going down a rabbit hole）那个行为经济学的在线课程。进展怎么样？</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">哥们儿，我简直<span style=\"background:#f5f0e6;color:#8b7355;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.98em\">上瘾了</span>。我一开始只是想<strong>温习一下</strong>（brush up on）一些工作上用得到的基础知识，但现在我已经学了六个模块了，凌晨两点还在看YouTube上的讲座。真的停不下来。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">哈，这很你。你一直都是那种会对各种稀奇古怪的东西<strong>狂热痴迷</strong>（geek out）的人。还记得你花了一整个夏天试图<strong>学会</strong>（get the hang of）编程吗？</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">好吧，说得没错。但这次不一样。那个教授讲解得特别好——就算是那些很深的理论内容，她也完全不会<strong>讲得让人听不懂</strong>（talk over your head）。她会用真实例子、表情包，什么都用上。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">那真是理想状态了。我大学时有个统计学教授，非常聪明但完全听不懂。什么东西都是<strong>左耳进右耳出</strong>（in one ear and out the other），因为他就是一个人在那里干巴巴地讲，完全没有上下文。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">是啊，一个好老师真的天差地别。说实话，到目前为止我最大的感悟就是，我以前只是<strong>了解了点皮毛</strong>（scratching the surface）。我以为自己对经济学还算了解，结果发现我几乎什么都不知道。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">至少你现在在<strong>下功夫</strong>（putting in the work）了。大多数人只会抱怨自己不懂，但从来不真的去做点什么。你在真的行动了。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">谢了，哥们。我在努力。唯一的缺点是我老在晚饭时提这些，我老婆就说：&quot;求你了，别再说了。&quot;我觉得她已经<strong>烦透了</strong>（sick and tired of）听我讲什么损失厌恶和沉没成本谬误。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">哈！经典。不过话说回来，人们不都说——<strong>知识就是力量</strong>（knowledge is power）嘛。只不过你可能别在吃意面的时候<strong>找她探讨</strong>（pick her brain）助推理论就好，你懂的？</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#e53935;white-space:nowrap\">B:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">好好好，<span style=\"background:#f5f0e6;color:#8b7355;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px;font-size:0.98em\">收到了</span>。那我以后都留着说给你听。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:5px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 6px 8px 0;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap\">A:</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:8px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333;line-height:1.7\">我真是太幸运了。</td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"background:#f3e5f5;border-left:4px solid #4a148c;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#4a148c;font-size:15px\">【本日表达列表】</strong></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">01.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>go down a rabbit hole</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 深入钻研某个话题，越挖越深，停不下来</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用 / 全球通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 聊到沉迷某个话题、网上冲浪越看越多时</span></td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">02.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>brush up on</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 温习、复习（已有但生疏的知识或技能）</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用 / 全球通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 准备考试、面试前复习旧知识时</span></td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">03.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>geek out (over something)</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 对某事物极度兴奋、热情投入地研究讨论</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 朋友之间聊到对某个爱好或话题特别痴迷时</span></td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">04.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>get the hang of</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 学会、掌握（某项技能的窍门）</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用 / 全球通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 谈论学习新技能的过程，如开车、做饭、用新软件等</span></td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">05.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>talk over someone&#x27;s head</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 讲得太深奥/太专业，让人听不懂</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 评价老师、演讲者是否通俗易懂时</span></td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">06.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>in one ear and out the other</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 左耳进右耳出，完全没记住</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用 / 全球通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 形容听了但没吸收，常用于上课、听讲座、被唠叨时</span></td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">07.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>scratch the surface</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 只了解皮毛、浅尝辄止</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用 / 全球通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 意识到某个领域远比自己以为的深广时</span></td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">08.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>put in the work</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 下功夫、付出努力</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 鼓励别人或肯定某人的努力付出时，常见于健身、学习、事业语境</span></td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">09.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>sick and tired of</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 烦透了、受够了</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用 / 全球通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 表达对反复出现的事情极度厌烦时</span></td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:6px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"28\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 8px 10px 14px;color:#1a73e8;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;white-space:nowrap;background:#f0f4ff;border-radius:8px 0 0 8px;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-right:none\">10.</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:10px 14px 10px 8px;background:#f8f9ff;border-radius:0 8px 8px 0;border:1px solid #d0d9ff;border-left:none\"><strong style=\"color:#1a73e8;font-size:14px\"><strong>pick someone&#x27;s brain</strong></strong><span style=\"color:#555;font-size:13px;margin-left:8px\">— 向某人请教、找人探讨以获取其见解</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f0fe;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#1a73e8;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">📍 美国通用</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;padding:2px 8px;background:#e8f5e9;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;color:#2e7d32;white-space:nowrap;margin-left:6px\">💬 想找有经验的人聊聊某个话题、获取建议时</span></td></tr></table>",
  "beauty": "<div style=\"background:#fce4ec;border-left:4px solid #e91e8c;padding:10px 16px;margin:18px 0 10px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0\"><strong style=\"color:#c2185b;font-size:15px\">【今日主题】</strong><span style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:400;color:#c2185b\">🌿 护肤小贴士 —— 橄榄皮「去暗提透」春季焕肤指南</span></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">三月下旬，换季敏感高发期。橄榄皮最容易在这个阶段出现&quot;黄上加灰&quot;的疲惫感。今天给你一套<strong>周日居家深层护理流程</strong>，重点解决角质偏厚、暗沉发黄、毛孔粗大三大核心问题。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">🧴 Step 1｜温和二次清洁（软化厚角质）</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span><strong>手法</strong>：洁面后，用浸湿化妆水的化妆棉，沿脸部轮廓<strong>由内向外、由下向上</strong>轻轻擦拭。</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span><strong>重点区域</strong>：鼻翼两侧、下颌线、额头发际线——这些是橄榄皮角质堆积最明显的地方。</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span><strong>频率</strong>：每周日做一次即可，不要天天擦拭，避免屏障受损。</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">&gt; ⚠️ 避开眼周，棉片不要反复来回摩擦，单方向轻抹。</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">🧪 Step 2｜分区酸类焕肤（去暗沉+缩毛孔）</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">角质层偏厚的皮肤对酸的耐受度相对较好，但依然要<strong>分区浓度管理</strong>：</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| 区域 | 推荐酸类 | 浓度建议 | 目的 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">|------|----------|----------|------|</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| T区（额+鼻） | <strong>水杨酸（BHA）</strong> | 1%\\~2% | 深入毛孔溶解油脂、缩孔 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| 两颊 | <strong>杏仁酸（Mandelic Acid）</strong> | 10%\\~15% | 温和提亮、改善暗黄 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| 下颌线/颈部 | <strong>乳糖酸（PHA）</strong> | 8%\\~10% | 保湿型去角质、改善粗糙暗沉 |</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span><strong>上脸顺序</strong>：先T区 → 两颊 → 下颌，涂薄层即可。</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span><strong>停留时间</strong>：初次10分钟，耐受后可延长至20分钟（非剥脱型直接留用过夜）。</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">💧 Step 3｜密集补水修复（锁住透亮感）</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">酸后皮肤通道打开，这时候补水效率翻倍：</p>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">1.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><strong>第一层 —— 小分子精华</strong>：含<strong>5% 烟酰胺 + 透明质酸钠</strong>的精华液，拍至吸收。烟酰胺对橄榄皮抑制黑色素转运效果极佳。</span></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">2.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><strong>第二层 —— 修护面霜</strong>：选含<strong>神经酰胺 + 角鲨烷</strong>的面霜，薄涂全脸，加固屏障。</span></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin:8px 0;padding:10px 14px;background:#fdf0f7;border-radius:8px\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;font-weight:700;min-width:70px;font-size:13px\">3.</span><span style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><strong>第三层 —— 封层（可选）</strong>：毛孔区域可以薄涂一层含<strong>积雪草</strong>成分的冻膜，敷15分钟后洗去，收敛镇定。</span></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">🌙 Step 4｜睡前加码（针对暗沉的夜间修复）</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>在面霜后，<strong>仅在苹果肌和额头中央</strong>点涂一层<strong>维A醇精华（0.3%~0.5%浓度）</strong>。</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>这是橄榄皮最容易&quot;灰暗&quot;的区域，长期坚持可以显著改善肤色均匀度和光泽感。</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>注意：维A醇和酸不要同一晚叠加使用。<strong>周日用酸，则维A放到周三、周五晚。</strong></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">💡 针对你的肤质/脸型：</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\"><strong>橄榄皮专属提醒：</strong></p>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>橄榄皮天然底色偏黄偏绿，千万<strong>不要追求&quot;白&quot;，而要追求&quot;透&quot;</strong>。护肤目标是让皮肤呈现健康的暖光泽感，而不是冷白。</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>烟酰胺是你的王牌成分——它不是让你变白，而是让色素分布更均匀，视觉上皮肤干净通透。</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>角质管理要坚持但不能过度：<strong>每周一次酸类即可</strong>，过度去角质反而会让皮肤变敏变红，橄榄皮一旦泛红会显得&quot;脏红&quot;而非&quot;好气色红&quot;。</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\"><strong>圆脸护肤附加技巧：</strong></p>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>涂面霜/精华时，手法配合<strong>提拉</strong>：双手从下巴沿下颌线向耳后推，从嘴角沿颧骨向太阳穴推。长期坚持可以帮助淋巴排水，视觉上收窄脸部轮廓。</div>\n<div style=\"padding:4px 0 4px 16px;color:#444;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7\"><span style=\"color:#e91e8c;margin-right:8px\">✦</span>周日可以加一个<strong>咬肌按摩</strong>：用指关节沿咬肌从下往上画圈30秒×3组，配合面油或面霜，帮助放松咬肌、柔化方圆感。</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<div style=\"color:#c2185b;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;margin:16px 0 6px;padding-bottom:4px;border-bottom:1px solid #fce4ec\">🎨 产品推荐（附理由）：</div>\n<div style=\"height:8px\"></div>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| 步骤 | 推荐产品 | 理由 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">|------|----------|------|</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| 二次清洁 | <strong>黛珂 紫苏水</strong>（化妆棉擦拭用） | 含紫苏叶提取物，消炎舒缓，擦拭后不紧绷 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| T区酸 | <strong>Paula&#x27;s Choice 2%水杨酸精华液</strong> | 经典BHA，质地清爽，控油缩孔效果稳定 |</p>\n<p style=\"margin:6px 0;line-height:1.8;color:#333;font-size:14px\">| 两颊酸 | **DR.WU 杏仁酸亮白</p>",
  "research": "<div style=\"background:#fff;border:1px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px;margin:16px 0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)\"><div style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#00bcd4,#00897b);color:#fff;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:6px;margin:-20px -22px 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1px\">📄 论文 1</div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#c62828;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📌 作者：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">HAO YANG, Joseph Foley</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#1565c0;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📖 标题：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;font-weight:700;\">Translanguaging as Interactional Resources Employed by Students in EFL Student-Led Group Task Interaction</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#00838f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📰 期刊：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Journal of English Language and Linguistics</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#e65100;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📅 年份：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">2024</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#2e7d32;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📊 引用量：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">2 次</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#4a148c;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📝 摘要：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">This study aimed to investigate the strategies used by students during group tasks in the EFL classroom. The study focused on translanguaging as one of the strategies to facilitate communication and interaction among students. The data was collected by recording the classroom discussions of a focused group in an EFL class at a Chinese university over three hours. The analysis was carried out using…</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#6a1b9a;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🔗 与本研究的关联性：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">该论文与<strong>方向二（课堂互动与中介）</strong>高度相关：研究聚焦EFL课堂中学生主导的小组任务互动，以会话分析方法考察translanguaging作为互动资源的使用策略，直接涉及translanguaging和peer interaction两个核心关键词。此外，研究情境设置在中国大学外语课堂，与CSL/语言教学课堂互动研究具有方法论和理论上的可迁移性，尤其在探究学习者如何通过多语资源协商意义、完成语言相关片段（LRE）方面可提供参照。</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#37474f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🆔 DOI：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7\"><a href=\"https://doi.org/10.62819/jel.2024.145\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;text-decoration:none\">🔍 10.62819/jel.2024.145</a></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:6px\"></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fff;border:1px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px;margin:16px 0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)\"><div style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#00bcd4,#00897b);color:#fff;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:6px;margin:-20px -22px 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1px\">📄 论文 2</div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#c62828;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📌 作者：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Richard Kern</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#1565c0;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📖 标题：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;font-weight:700;\">Twenty‐first century technologies and language education: Charting a path forward</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#00838f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📰 期刊：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Modern Language Journal</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#e65100;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📅 年份：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">2024</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#2e7d32;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📊 引用量：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">55 次</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#4a148c;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📝 摘要：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">The COVID-19 pandemic, necessitating remote instruction in the vast majority of educational institutions around the world, put technology squarely at the center of language learning and teaching. Virtually all teaching and learning was mediated by Zoom or similar videoconferencing platforms. Students could see one another&#x27;s faces (rather than the backs of their peers’ heads), but they could also c…</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#6a1b9a;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🔗 与本研究的关联性：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">这篇论文聚焦于21世纪技术（尤其是疫情期间远程教学平台）对语言教育的影响，与用户的研究方向存在间接关联。首先，远程教学中视频会议平台的使用改变了课堂互动模式（如聊天窗口作为交际副渠道、分组讨论室中的同伴互动），这与方向二关注的CSL课堂互动、同伴互动及语言相关片段（LRE）研究相呼应，技术中介的互动可视为一种新的中介形式。其次，技术对教学实践的深层变革也可能影响教师的情感</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#37474f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🆔 DOI：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7\"><a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1111/modl.12924\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;text-decoration:none\">🔍 10.1111/modl.12924</a></td></tr></table>\n<div style=\"height:6px\"></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fff;border:1px solid #e0e0e0;border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px;margin:16px 0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06)\"><div style=\"background:linear-gradient(135deg,#00bcd4,#00897b);color:#fff;padding:10px 16px;border-radius:6px;margin:-20px -22px 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;letter-spacing:1px\">📄 论文 3</div>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#c62828;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📌 作者：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Kevin W. H. Tai</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#1565c0;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📖 标题：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;font-weight:700;\">Translanguaging as Inclusive Pedagogical Practices in English-Medium Instruction Science and Mathematics Classrooms for Linguistically and Culturally Diverse Students</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#00838f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📰 期刊：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Research in Science Education</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#e65100;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📅 年份：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">2021</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#2e7d32;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📊 引用量：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">120 次</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#4a148c;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">📝 摘要：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">Abstract In English-medium instruction (EMI), English-as-a-second-language students will learn all/some subjects through English. Although there are a considerable number of studies which explore classroom interaction in Hong Kong (HK) secondary EMI schools, few studies have investigated EMI lessons which involve South Asian ethnic minorised students. These students share different linguistic and …</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#6a1b9a;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🔗 与本研究的关联性：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#333;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;\">该论文直接关联<strong>方向二</strong>，研究EMI课堂中translanguaging作为包容性教学策略的使用，涉及课堂互动分析，与CSL/多语课堂中translanguaging的理论框架和互动分析方法高度契合。论文聚焦语言文化多元背景下的少数族裔学生，呼应方向二中对同伴互动及语言中介过程的关注，尤其是多模态会话分析方法可与LRE、MICM等微观互动研究形成方法论对话。此外，研究涉及EMI制度背景下教师如何回应学生的语言多样性，也间接关联**</td></tr></table>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:7px 0;border-collapse:collapse\"><tr><td width=\"88\" valign=\"top\" style=\"color:#37474f;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding-right:8px;white-space:nowrap\">🆔 DOI：</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7\"><a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1007/s11165-021-10018-6\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#1a73e8;text-decoration:none\">🔍 10.1007/s11165-021-10018-6</a></td></tr></table>\n</div>"
}